### Data Deletion Request

If you wish to delete your Data for the **Meanwhile App**, please follow these steps:

1. Email us at spprt.at.meanwhile@gmail.com with the subject line: "Data Deletion Request".
2. Include the email address or Spotify User ID associated with your account.
3. Specify if you want all associated data (e.g., chat messages, uploaded photos) to be deleted.

#### Data Retention Policy
- Upon account deletion, we will remove all personal data, including your username, profile picture, and Spotify-linked data.
- For compliance reasons, some data may be retained for up to 30 days (e.g., logs or records for fraud detection).

If you have further questions, contact us at spprt.at.meanwhile@gmail.com
